Class ObjectSearchableFiniteMetricSpace<T>

java.lang.Object
  edu.stanford.math.plex4.metric.impl.ObjectSearchableFiniteMetricSpace<T>
Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:
AbstractIntMetricSpace, AbstractObjectMetric<T>, AbstractObjectMetricSpace<T>, AbstractSearchableMetricSpace<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
EuclideanMetricSpace, KDEuclideanMetricSpace
public abstract class ObjectSearchableFiniteMetricSpace<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractSearchableMetricSpace<T>

This class implements the AbstractSearchableMetricSpace interface over type T. It stores the elements of the metric space as an array.

Author:
Andrew Tausz
